milestones.description: Carlyon and Greenwood's 60-run partnership is JER's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 36 between Carlyon and Greenwood
Rohan Mustafa has broken the record for most ducks (8) in ODIs for UAE, going past Zahoor Khan's 7
Sumerauer has become the top wicket-taker for JER in ODIs with 11 wickets, going past Perchard's 7
Carlyon has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (58) in an innings in ODIs for JER, going past Lawrenson's 56
Carlyon has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (5) in ODIs for JER, going past Greenwood's 2
Carlyon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for JER, going past Jake Dunford
